headline: Fed Meeting, Apple, Meta, GM, Boeing, Chevron, and More to Watch This Week
summary: A big week for earnings will see reports from Microsoft, Exxon, Visa, GE Vernova, and many more. The Fed is expected to keep rates steady, as Jerome Powell closes out his final months as Chair.
